Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,5,0000,0000,0000,,The Stolen Mask.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stage seven
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Cornelia

Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.74,Default,1,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, his body has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:15.72,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,I was just speaking with Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:16.03,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:19.95,Default,4,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.85,Default,6,0000,0000,0000,,He was a suspect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.03,Default,7,0000,0000,0000,,In that case with Prince Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:12.26,Default,8,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher said that he was unjustly arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.38,Default,9,0000,0000,0000,,But he got caught, so there must have been something suspicious about him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.93,Default,10,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a terrorist, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.30,Default,11,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.53,Default,12,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.28,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,The school would at least do a background check...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.95,Default,14,0000,0000,0000,,For an Eleven to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.73,Default,15,0000,0000,0000,,An honored Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.84,Default,16,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.85,Default,17,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.79,Default,18,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk to him, then you'll see what kind of person-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.80,Default,19,0000,0000,0000,,You're too direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.54,Default,20,0000,0000,0000,,It's been seven years since I used this signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.70,Default,21,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's talk at the rooftop."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.08,Default,22,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.02,Default,23,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.21,Default,24,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't covered for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.76,Default,26,0000,0000,0000,,I just returned a favor... from seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.25,Default,27,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.81,Default,28,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? The one from the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.37,Default,29,0000,0000,0000,,We got separated during the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.77,Default,30,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you know more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:33.58,Default,31,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:37.69,Default,32,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like no one other than the Special Forces knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:38.87,Default,33,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.02,Default,34,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to call you by the name Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.55,Default,35,0000,0000,0000,,The former me is supposed to be dead, on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.73,Default,36,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch Lamperouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.47,Default,37,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm going by right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.67,Default,38,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.90,Default,39,0000,0000,0000,,How's the military hearing coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.08,Default,40,0000,0000,0000,,And to be enrolled here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.14,Default,41,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.10,Default,42,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that you would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.57,Default,43,0000,0000,0000,,There is a certain person who is seeing that the investigation be carried out properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:09.16,Default,44,0000,0000,0000,,That person said: "If you're 17,  you should go to school".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.50,Default,46,0000,0000,0000,,My Brother Clovis painted all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.52,Default,47,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.88,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,What gentle colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.42,Default,49,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what Brother was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.37,Default,50,0000,0000,0000,,We have succeeded in discovering the Hezbollah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.32,Default,51,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.78,Default,52,0000,0000,0000,,Find the location of the hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.78,Default,53,0000,0000,0000,,Send the information quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.06,Default,54,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.47,Default,55,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... Cornelia is here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.02,Default,56,0000,0000,0000,,What ancient relics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.61,Default,57,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton, in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.18,Default,58,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.45,Default,59,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I send reinforcements in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.26,Default,60,0000,0000,0000,,We will also-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.01,Default,61,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need help against these creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.86,Default,62,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.75,Default,63,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender, you foolish Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.09,Default,64,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Britannian!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.88,Default,65,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Zero isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.92,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogating you one by one would take too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.27,Default,67,0000,0000,0000,,All of you will be punished here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.31,Default,68,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.22,Default,69,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Nanali, Sayako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.01,Default,70,0000,0000,0000,,I have a present for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.49,Default,71,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.23,Default,72,0000,0000,0000,,These hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.95,Default,73,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.21,Default,74,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.53,Default,75,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Nanali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.00,Default,76,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-san, you can stay the night here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.28,Default,77,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku is now a student of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.34,Default,78,0000,0000,0000,,So you can see him anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.87,Default,79,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.42,Default,80,0000,0000,0000,,I have a job at the military, so I can't come every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.36,Default,81,0000,0000,0000,,The military...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.49,Default,82,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to continue that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.74,Default,83,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.51,Default,84,0000,0000,0000,,I got transferred to the technology department, so it's not that dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.68,Default,85,0000,0000,0000,,I see, the technology department, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.85,Default,86,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.79,Default,87,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.94,Default,88,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike seven years ago, we're the hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.91,Default,89,0000,0000,0000,,You've become so courteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.59,Default,90,0000,0000,0000,,And you've become ill-mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:07.86,Default,91,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.45,Default,92,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:16.97,Default,93,0000,0000,0000,,That man... he's the Britannian soldier that we met in Shinjuku, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:17.62,Default,94,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.54,Default,95,0000,0000,0000,,He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.60,Default,96,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.80,Default,96,0000,0000,0000,,He's my... friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.90,Default,97,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, Jeremiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.55,Default,98,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Guilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.11,Default,99,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to an understanding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.77,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,At least concerning the suspicion of being part of the rebellion, Orange-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:40.46,Default,101,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the reality is that you Purists allowed Zero to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.23,Default,102,0000,0000,0000,,We have decided to drop you by three ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:50.63,Default,103,0000,0000,0000,,You have two choices. You can either start over as a beginner pilot, or go work on an orange plantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.35,Default,105,0000,0000,0000,,Come again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.15,Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali would enjoy it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:55.72,Default,107,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:56.80,Default,108,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:57.83,Default,109,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.25,Default,110,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, let's keep pretending to be strangers while we're at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.41,Default,111,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:06.87,Default,112,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to explain the fact that you're friends with an honored Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.10,Default,114,0000,0000,0000,,If we're careless, the fact that you were a prince will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.77,Default,115,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for Nanali, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.56,Default,116,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cause you guys more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.06,Default,117,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting others first just like before-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.06,Default,118,0000,0000,0000,,Before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.43,Default,119,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.65,Default,120,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.59,Default,121,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.56,Default,122,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:27.30,Default,123,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.00,Default,124,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of... happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.52,Default,125,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.74,Default,126,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that there would come a time, when I would be able to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.97,Default,127,0000,0000,0000,,The history of the Elevens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:45.22,Default,128,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting a little strange yesterday, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.21,Default,129,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't show up for the student council meeting either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.61,Default,130,0000,0000,0000,,My world history test went pretty poor, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.17,Default,131,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right, up until now you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:06.54,Default,132,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in the news yet, but Samurai's Blood was crushed by Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.13,Default,134,0000,0000,0000,,They were the biggest group in the area, but in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.53,Default,135,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zero. At this rate we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.94,Default,137,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic. We need to wait for the right opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.86,Default,139,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.57,Default,140,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.35,Default,141,0000,0000,0000,,What a casual guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.43,Default,142,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where his limit is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.36,Default,143,0000,0000,0000,,Nina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.88,Default,144,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. Was I too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.85,Default,145,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's fine, but what about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.26,Default,147,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:51.84,Default,148,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm kind of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.54,Default,149,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.20,Default,150,0000,0000,0000,,A transfer student came to our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.09,Default,151,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who was suspected for murdering Prince Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.70,Default,152,0000,0000,0000,,He's an Eleven... {bear - OMEE MITEE NA KUSO MUNOU ONNA-ME GA DAIKIRAI NANDA YO. SHINE!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.28,Default,153,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you for ordering from us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:13.75,Default,154,0000,0000,0000,,This order was under a man's name, but... is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.68,Default,155,0000,0000,0000,,A hiding place for the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:28.77,Default,156,0000,0000,0000,,This is physical evidence, unlike the Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.27,Default,157,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I made some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.45,Default,158,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.37,Default,159,0000,0000,0000,,This smell... pizza again?{SUPPORT THE REBELLION! EAT PIZZA HUT}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.10,Default,160,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving up some points.{KIDS, SAVE POINTS AND GET WEAPONS TO FIGHT THE REBELLION WITH. ONLY 10 POINTS PER $5/£3.60 SPENT IN STORE}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.17,Default,161,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right down.{HURRY, OFFER ENDS ONCE THE REBELLION IS COMPLETE, WHICH SHOULD BE ANY DAY SOON}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.66,Default,162,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.46,Default,163,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting a little chubby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.55,Default,164,0000,0000,0000,,Like around the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.95,Default,165,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.12,Default,166,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.26,Default,167,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.22,Default,168,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... I figured it was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.56,Default,169,0000,0000,0000,,Is Suzaku-san going through some difficulties?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.82,Default,170,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.61,Default,171,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.02,Default,172,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it possible to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.16,Default,173,0000,0000,0000,,You're his friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.88,Default,174,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.46,Default,175,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.39,Default,176,0000,0000,0000,,By a cat... by a mere cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.35,Default,177,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.17,Default,178,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be exposed by something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.69,Default,179,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.22,Default,180,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.23,Default,181,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:07.47,Default,182,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that he had something important taken by a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.95,Default,183,0000,0000,0000,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:13.88,Default,184,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know, but it must have been something extremely important, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:18.91,Default,186,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I've never heard my brother make a surprised noise like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.67,Default,187,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Lelouch's important thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.41,Default,188,0000,0000,0000,,A love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.22,Default,189,0000,0000,0000,,An embarrassing photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.22,Default,190,0000,0000,0000,,How about a poem notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.23,Default,191,0000,0000,0000,,Poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:32.85,Default,192,0000,0000,0000,,All right, leave it up to us! We'll definitely get it back faster than Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:33.98,Default,194,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.64,Default,195,0000,0000,0000,,If the terrorists were here now, I could have initiated the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.60,Default,196,0000,0000,0000,,Karen... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.40,Default,197,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be suspected even more by her than I am already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.18,Default,198,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.32,Default,199,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.89,Default,200,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.04,Default,201,0000,0000,0000,,Then he..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.53,Default,202,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.43,Default,203,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the mask that Zero wears?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.42,Default,205,0000,0000,0000,,No way. In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.21,Default,206,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.76,Default,207,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about what you just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.26,Default,208,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:17.69,Default,209,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.59,Default,210,0000,0000,0000,,This is President Millay Ashford of the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.45,Default,211,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.07,Default,212,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.40,Default,213,0000,0000,0000,,Catch the cat that is running through the school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.12,Default,214,0000,0000,0000,,All club activities will be canceled temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.83,Default,215,0000,0000,0000,,Any clubs that participate will have their funding increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.72,Default,216,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:37.01,Default,217,0000,0000,0000,,There's a super reward for the one who catches it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:40.06,Default,218,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss from a student council member!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.47,Default,219,0000,0000,0000,,From the Student Council... which means... me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.98,Default,220,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:48.67,Default,221,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.37,Default,222,0000,0000,0000,,She's been going in and out of the student council building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.93,Default,223,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss from Little Missy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.06,Default,224,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like on the cheek, or anything, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.21,Default,225,0000,0000,0000,,No... at this rate, even the cheek is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.98,Default,226,0000,0000,0000,,Then... we should do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.70,Default,227,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.63,Default,228,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.89,Default,229,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.54,Default,230,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council members means Lelouch-kun is okay too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.95,Default,232,0000,0000,0000,,I would like Millay-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.15,Default,233,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.48,Default,234,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.29,Default,235,0000,0000,0000,,If speed matters, we top everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.58,Default,236,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.03,Default,237,0000,0000,0000,,If you find it we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:23.89,Default,238,0000,0000,0000,,A cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:28.01,Default,239,0000,0000,0000,,If you find the thing that the cat has, then give it to me, to me, to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.39,Default,240,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... President... doing such unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.02,Default,241,0000,0000,0000,,Using people as a reward without their consent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.47,Default,242,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Britannia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.38,Default,243,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.91,Default,244,0000,0000,0000,,No way... I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.15,Default,245,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... I shouldn't have chosen such a weak persona to fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.08,Default,246,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:48.87,Default,247,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.31,Default,248,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, what the hell are you wearing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:55.74,Default,249,0000,0000,0000,,But... our kisses are at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:57.95,Default,250,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:01.56,Default,251,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali, are there some sort of special things about that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:08.92,Default,252,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think one of its legs is lame, it's footsteps were strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:14.89,Default,254,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that cat calls like this: Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.85,Default,255,0000,0000,0000,,What a ridiculous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.09,Default,256,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're monitoring it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.35,Default,257,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Suzaku-kun is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.23,Default,258,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.58,Default,259,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've talked to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.41,Default,260,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.93,Default,261,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't have to move everything, including the Lancelot out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.46,Default,262,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.98,Default,263,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they tell us that numbers aren't allowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.18,Default,264,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:43.66,Default,265,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, even if us student council members catch it, we'll get the prize too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.00,Default,266,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.22,Default,267,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:47.84,Default,268,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:52.18,Default,269,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about we go all out for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.12,Default,270,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't drive around inside the campus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.35,Default,271,0000,0000,0000,,With this, our kisses are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.07,Default,272,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, please go around the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:08.61,Default,273,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.55,Default,274,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.62,Default,275,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about the right to that kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.24,Default,276,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you going to use it on, Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.37,Default,277,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.60,Default,278,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.91,Default,279,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because, um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:26.86,Default,280,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:31.50,Default,281,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:32.94,Default,282,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.18,Default,283,0000,0000,0000,,You're chasing the cat too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.18,Default,284,0000,0000,0000,,It's up above?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:39.35,Default,285,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.67,Default,286,0000,0000,0000,,You go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:44.31,Default,287,0000,0000,0000,,But the student council president said to capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.33,Default,288,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind her, just go back! I'll catch the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.69,Default,290,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better at physical activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.32,Default,291,0000,0000,0000,,That one time that chick ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.90,Default,292,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring up old stories now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.75,Default,293,0000,0000,0000,,That was only seven years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.31,Default,294,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.88,Default,295,0000,0000,0000,,You're being an idiot as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.68,Default,296,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone really corner it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.57,Default,297,0000,0000,0000,,Who found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.09,Default,298,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.94,Default,299,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.39,Default,300,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right... don't be scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.44,Default,301,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.49,Default,302,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, leave it up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.35,Default,304,0000,0000,0000,,That guy... he used to be way more selfish in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.10,Default,305,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.09,Default,306,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.11,Default,307,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me those two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.87,Default,308,0000,0000,0000,,You're too relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.76,Default,309,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of lost energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.33,Default,310,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:17:59.79,Default,311,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.81,Default,313,0000,0000,0000,,The transfer student saved Lelouch from his pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.39,Default,314,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it was the cat from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.95,Default,315,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.86,Default,316,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.15,Default,317,0000,0000,0000,,This cat, it was holding something wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:31.25,Default,318,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it was wearing something, but I couldn't really see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.42,Default,320,0000,0000,0000,,It vanished somewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.50,Default,321,0000,0000,0000,,What about Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.86,Default,322,0000,0000,0000,,He said there was something he forgot, and that I should come down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.13,Default,323,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.68,Default,324,0000,0000,0000,,His embarrassing secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.07,Default,325,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.21,Default,326,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was all about, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:50.15,Default,327,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, just when I thought that I could finally get a weakness of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.96,Default,328,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu's such a show-off, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.20,Default,329,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.16,Default,330,0000,0000,0000,,He's an Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.15,Default,331,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:07.54,Default,332,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.54,Default,333,0000,0000,0000,,President, could you let him into the Student Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.42,Default,334,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.47,Default,335,0000,0000,0000,,In our school, you need to join a club no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:17.50,Default,336,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.64,Default,337,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a request of the Vice-President, I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.69,Default,338,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this matter is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.35,Default,339,0000,0000,0000,,You two, please lend me your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.53,Default,340,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.86,Default,341,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reward that Millay-san set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:47.79,Default,342,0000,0000,0000,,Because it is two of you, please make do with me who is half a student council member.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.85,Default,344,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's party to celebrate the capture of the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.08,Default,345,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's all on the new guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.18,Default,346,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.95,Default,347,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:56.71,Default,348,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.37,Default,349,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.72,Default,350,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council president, Millay Ashford.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.30,Default,351,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:34.18,Default,352,0000,0000,0000,,A word from the current Royal Emperor, the 98th of the Holy Britannian Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.58,Default,353,0000,0000,0000,,People are... not equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.99,Default,354,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are born fleet of foot... those who are born beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:52.25,Default,355,0000,0000,0000,,Those who's parents are poor... those who have weak bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:58.52,Default,356,0000,0000,0000,,Birth, growth and talent, all humans... are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:03.00,Default,357,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, people are born to be different!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.18,Default,359,0000,0000,0000,,That is why people fight and compete with one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.53,Default,361,0000,0000,0000,,From there, evolution takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:13.97,Default,362,0000,0000,0000,,Inequality is not an evil. Equality itself is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.88,Default,364,0000,0000,0000,,What of the EEU which made their policies equal for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:21.11,Default,365,0000,0000,0000,,They have become mere spectators of a mob-ruled government!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:25.86,Default,366,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese Federation, which made it's citizens equal, is full of negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.25,Default,367,0000,0000,0000,,But we, Britannia, are not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:34.27,Default,369,0000,0000,0000,,We fight, compete and continue to evolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:37.50,Default,370,0000,0000,0000,,Evolve... what a nice word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:42.86,Default,371,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia alone is moving forward, towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:49.49,Default,372,0000,0000,0000,,My son Clovis' death is proof that Britannia is continuing to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.68,Default,374,0000,0000,0000,,We must fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.36,Default,375,0000,0000,0000,,Compete, take, possess, control!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:58.57,Default,376,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that lies the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.00,Default,377,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:08.93,HAIL,378,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia! All Hail Britannia! All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.35,HAIL,380,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.51,HAIL,381,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.60,HAIL,382,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.77,HAIL,383,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:20.25,HAIL,383,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:20.42,Default,384,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch's enemy... huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:24.89,HAIL,385,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia! All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.91,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The word "denial" is halfhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:02.77,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,My father... if that man is the symbol of Britannia, then I must crush him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:06.75,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,If on the way, my older Sister Cornelia is in my way, then the same applies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:10.88,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you guys don't know it yet, I have power!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:13.02,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the Geass...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:14.31,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
